{start_of_verse: Verse 1}
[C]JUST WHEN I NEEDED YOU  YOU LEFT AND WENT [F]AWAY
[C]YOU MADE MY LIFE SO BLUE BOTH NIGHT AND [G7]DAY
[C]YOU LEFT ME HERE BEHIND WITH A TROUBLED WORRIED [F]MIND
[C]SO BROKEN HEARTED [G7]TOO  JUST WHEN I NEEDED [C]YOU
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_verse: Verse 2}
