[G7]AND NEVER CALL YOUR NAME  WHAT A SHAME  WHAT A [C]SHAME
[F]YOU'RE THE ONE WHO WAS TO [C]BLAME
[F]YOU'RE THE ONE WHO [C]WAS UNTRUE [G7]JUST WHEN I NEEDED [C]YOU
{end_of_verse}

